    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/quotes_and_excerpts/engineer_creativity/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/quotes_and_excerpts/engineer_creativity/</guid>
      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;The cost of software&#xA;maintenance increases with the square of&#xA;the programmer’s creativity.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&amp;ndash; &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Robert D Bliss&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/quotes_and_excerpts/self_supporting/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/quotes_and_excerpts/self_supporting/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div id=&#34;outline-container-headline-1&#34; class=&#34;outline-3&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;headline-1&#34;&gt;&#xA;From the Unix Philosophy Page&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div id=&#34;outline-text-headline-1&#34; class=&#34;outline-text-3&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&lt;em&gt;.. When your tools shape your work, you feel friction instantly and you fix it.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;—&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&lt;em&gt;.. Constraint is not a hardship. It is a design instrument.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;—&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;.. Iteration is the real productivity engine. When you can change something and&#xA;see the result quickly, you learn what works.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;—&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Keep the system small enough to understand.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;—&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Let programs stay replaceable. The future you can&amp;#39;t predict arrives anyway. Parts&#xA;that can be swapped out survice change.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/quotes_and_excerpts/what_the_hell/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
